{
  "video_id": "kiUnJ1d8vvw",
  "title": "Jay Silver: Hack a banana, make a keyboard!",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12714.0,
      "end_time": 14410.0,
      "text": "Hey guys."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14410.0,
      "end_time": 15811.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s funny, someone just mentioned MacGyver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 15811.0,
      "end_time": 17751.0,
      "text": "because that was, like, I loved it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 17751.0,
      "end_time": 23710.0,
      "text": "and when I was seven, I taped a fork to a drill"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23710.0,
      "end_time": 25792.0,
      "text": "and I was like, \"Hey, Mom, I&#39;m going to Olive Garden.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25792.0,
      "end_time": 29943.0,
      "text": "And -- (Drilling noise) (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29943.0,
      "end_time": 32875.0,
      "text": "And it worked really well there."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32875.0,
      "end_time": 36696.0,
      "text": "And you know, it had a profound effect on me."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36696.0,
      "end_time": 38924.0,
      "text": "It sounds silly, but I thought, okay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38924.0,
      "end_time": 41796.0,
      "text": "the way the world works can be changed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41796.0,
      "end_time": 43947.0,
      "text": "and it can be changed by me in these small ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43947.0,
      "end_time": 45661.0,
      "text": "And my relationship to"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45661.0,
      "end_time": 47153.0,
      "text": "especially human-made objects"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47153.0,
      "end_time": 49380.0,
      "text": "which someone else said they work like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49380.0,
      "end_time": 52187.0,
      "text": "well, I can say they work a different way, a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52188.0,
      "end_time": 54686.0,
      "text": "And so, about 20 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54686.0,
      "end_time": 56194.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t realize the full effect of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56194.0,
      "end_time": 57971.0,
      "text": "but I went to Costa Rica"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57971.0,
      "end_time": 60138.0,
      "text": "and I stayed with these Guaymí natives there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60138.0,
      "end_time": 63640.0,
      "text": "and they could pull leaves off of trees and make shingles out of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63640.0,
      "end_time": 66809.0,
      "text": "and they could make beds out of trees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66809.0,
      "end_time": 69420.0,
      "text": "and they could -- I watched this woman for three days."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 69430.0,
      "end_time": 72290.0,
      "text": "I was there. She was peeling this palm frond apart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72290.0,
      "end_time": 75427.0,
      "text": "these little threads off of it, and she&#39;d roll the threads together"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75427.0,
      "end_time": 78145.0,
      "text": "and make little thicker threads, like strings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78145.0,
      "end_time": 80966.0,
      "text": "and she would weave the strings together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80966.0,
      "end_time": 84446.0,
      "text": "and as the materiality of this exact very bag"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84446.0,
      "end_time": 87334.0,
      "text": "formed before my eyes over those three days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87334.0,
      "end_time": 90641.0,
      "text": "the materiality of the way the world works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 90641.0,
      "end_time": 93115.0,
      "text": "of reality, kind of started to unravel in my mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93115.0,
      "end_time": 96463.0,
      "text": "because I realized that this bag and these clothes"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96463.0,
      "end_time": 98847.0,
      "text": "and the trampoline you have at home and the pencil sharpener,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98847.0,
      "end_time": 102979.0,
      "text": "everything you have is made out of either a tree or a rock"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 102980.0,
      "end_time": 105324.0,
      "text": "or something we dug out of the ground and did some process to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105324.0,
      "end_time": 109235.0,
      "text": "maybe a more complicated one, but still, everything was made that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109235.0,
      "end_time": 111426.0,
      "text": "And so I had to start studying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111427.0,
      "end_time": 113137.0,
      "text": "who is it that&#39;s making these decisions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113137.0,
      "end_time": 114946.0,
      "text": "Who&#39;s making these things? How did they make them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114946.0,
      "end_time": 116440.0,
      "text": "What stops us from making them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116440.0,
      "end_time": 119345.0,
      "text": "Because this is how reality is created."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119345.0,
      "end_time": 121932.0,
      "text": "So I started right away. I was at MIT Media Lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121932.0,
      "end_time": 124481.0,
      "text": "and I was studying the maker movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124481.0,
      "end_time": 126300.0,
      "text": "and makers and creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 126310.0,
      "end_time": 128158.0,
      "text": "And I started in nature, because I saw these Guaymís"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 128157.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131202.0,
      "text": "doing it in nature, and there just seems to be less barriers."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 131203.0,
      "end_time": 134548.0,
      "text": "So I went to Vermont to Not Back to School Camp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 134548.0,
      "end_time": 137800.0,
      "text": "where there&#39;s unschoolers who are just kind of hanging out"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 137800.0,
      "end_time": 139287.0,
      "text": "and willing to try anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 139287.0,
      "end_time": 141580.0,
      "text": "So I said, \"Let&#39;s go into the woods near this stream"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 141580.0,
      "end_time": 143609.0,
      "text": "and just put stuff together, you know, make something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 143609.0,
      "end_time": 146196.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t care, geometrical shapes, just grab some junk from around you."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 146196.0,
      "end_time": 147845.0,
      "text": "We won&#39;t bring anything with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 147845.0,
      "end_time": 150364.0,
      "text": "And, like, within minutes, this is very easy for adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150364.0,
      "end_time": 151452.0,
      "text": "and teens to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 151452.0,
      "end_time": 154587.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a triangle that was being formed underneath a flowing stream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 154587.0,
      "end_time": 157171.0,
      "text": "and the shape of an oak leaf being made"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 157171.0,
      "end_time": 160364.0,
      "text": "by other small oak leaves being put together."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 160365.0,
      "end_time": 163102.0,
      "text": "A leaf tied to a stick with a blade of grass."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 163102.0,
      "end_time": 165798.0,
      "text": "The materiality and fleshiness and meat of the mushroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 165798.0,
      "end_time": 169170.0,
      "text": "being explored by how it can hold up different objects being stuck into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 169170.0,
      "end_time": 172734.0,
      "text": "And after about 45 minutes, you get really intricate projects"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 172735.0,
      "end_time": 175962.0,
      "text": "like leaves sorted by hue, so you get a color fade"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 175962.0,
      "end_time": 177805.0,
      "text": "and put in a circle like a wreath."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 177806.0,
      "end_time": 180422.0,
      "text": "And the creator of this, he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 180422.0,
      "end_time": 182910.0,
      "text": "\"This is fire. I call this fire.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 182920.0,
      "end_time": 184319.0,
      "text": "And someone asked him, \"How do you get those sticks"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 184319.0,
      "end_time": 186790.0,
      "text": "to stay on that tree?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 186800.0,
      "end_time": 189190.0,
      "text": "And he&#39;s like, \"I don&#39;t know, but I can show you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 189190.0,
      "end_time": 190822.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m like, \"Wow, that&#39;s really amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 190822.0,
      "end_time": 192205.0,
      "text": "He doesn&#39;t know, but he can show you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192205.0,
      "end_time": 194785.0,
      "text": "So his hands know and his intuition knows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 194785.0,
      "end_time": 197641.0,
      "text": "but sometimes what we know gets in the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 197641.0,
      "end_time": 199678.0,
      "text": "of what could be, especially"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 199678.0,
      "end_time": 202605.0,
      "text": "when it comes to the human-made, human-built world."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 202605.0,
      "end_time": 204902.0,
      "text": "We think we already know how something works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 204902.0,
      "end_time": 207450.0,
      "text": "so we can&#39;t imagine how it could work."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 207450.0,
      "end_time": 208391.0,
      "text": "We know how it&#39;s supposed to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 208391.0,
      "end_time": 211798.0,
      "text": "so we can&#39;t suppose all the things that could be possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 211798.0,
      "end_time": 215645.0,
      "text": "So kids don&#39;t have as hard of a time with this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 215645.0,
      "end_time": 218930.0,
      "text": "and I saw in my own son, I gave him this book."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 218930.0,
      "end_time": 221138.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a good hippie dad, so I&#39;m like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 221138.0,
      "end_time": 223315.0,
      "text": "\"Okay, you&#39;re going to learn to love the moon."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 223315.0,
      "end_time": 225648.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to give you some building blocks"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 225648.0,
      "end_time": 228798.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re nonrectilinear cactus building blocks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 228798.0,
      "end_time": 230612.0,
      "text": "so it&#39;s totally legit.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 230612.0,
      "end_time": 232886.0,
      "text": "But he doesn&#39;t really know what to do with these."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 232886.0,
      "end_time": 234458.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t show him."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 234458.0,
      "end_time": 235966.0,
      "text": "And so he&#39;s like, \"Okay, I&#39;ll just mess around with this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 235966.0,
      "end_time": 239869.0,
      "text": "This is no different than the sticks are to the teens in the forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 239869.0,
      "end_time": 242341.0,
      "text": "Just going to try to put them in shapes"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 242341.0,
      "end_time": 244117.0,
      "text": "and push on them and stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 244117.0,
      "end_time": 246780.0,
      "text": "And before long, he&#39;s kind of got this mechanism"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 246781.0,
      "end_time": 250451.0,
      "text": "where you can almost launch and catapult objects around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 250451.0,
      "end_time": 252715.0,
      "text": "and he enlists us in helping him."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 252716.0,
      "end_time": 254651.0,
      "text": "And at this point, I&#39;m starting to wonder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 254651.0,
      "end_time": 257452.0,
      "text": "what kind of tools can we give people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 257452.0,
      "end_time": 260406.0,
      "text": "especially adults, who know too much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 260406.0,
      "end_time": 262697.0,
      "text": "so that they can see the world as malleable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 262697.0,
      "end_time": 264174.0,
      "text": "so they see themselves as agents of change"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 264174.0,
      "end_time": 265635.0,
      "text": "in their everyday lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 265636.0,
      "end_time": 268122.0,
      "text": "Because the most advanced scientists are really"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 268122.0,
      "end_time": 270854.0,
      "text": "just kind of pushing the way the world itself works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 270854.0,
      "end_time": 272310.0,
      "text": "pushing what matter can do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 272310.0,
      "end_time": 274812.0,
      "text": "the most advanced artists are just pushing the medium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 274812.0,
      "end_time": 276758.0,
      "text": "and any sufficiently complicated task,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 276758.0,
      "end_time": 279683.0,
      "text": "whether you&#39;re a cook or a carpenter or you&#39;re raising a child --"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 279683.0,
      "end_time": 281369.0,
      "text": "anything that&#39;s complicated --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 281369.0,
      "end_time": 283896.0,
      "text": "comes up with problems that aren&#39;t solved in the middle of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 283896.0,
      "end_time": 287222.0,
      "text": "and you can&#39;t do a good job getting it done unless you can say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 287222.0,
      "end_time": 289349.0,
      "text": "\"Okay, well we&#39;re just going to have to refigure this."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 289350.0,
      "end_time": 292290.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t care that pencils are supposed to be for writing."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 292290.0,
      "end_time": 294214.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to use them a different way.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 294214.0,
      "end_time": 299130.0,
      "text": "So let me show you a little demo."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 299130.0,
      "end_time": 303575.0,
      "text": "This is a little piano circuit right in here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 303575.0,
      "end_time": 305666.0,
      "text": "and this is an ordinary paintbrush"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 305666.0,
      "end_time": 308661.0,
      "text": "that I smashed it together with. (Beeping)"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 308661.0,
      "end_time": 310524.0,
      "text": "And so, with some ketchup,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 310524.0,
      "end_time": 313998.0,
      "text": "— (musical notes) —"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 313998.0,
      "end_time": 315287.0,
      "text": "and then I can kind of"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 315287.0,
      "end_time": 321782.0,
      "text": "— (musical notes) —"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 321782.0,
      "end_time": 323741.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 323741.0,
      "end_time": 326464.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s awesome, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 326464.0,
      "end_time": 327774.0,
      "text": "But this is not what&#39;s awesome."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 327774.0,
      "end_time": 329336.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s awesome is what happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 329336.0,
      "end_time": 332755.0,
      "text": "when you give the piano circuit to people."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 332755.0,
      "end_time": 334138.0,
      "text": "A pencil is not just a pencil."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 334138.0,
      "end_time": 335806.0,
      "text": "Look what it has in the middle of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 335806.0,
      "end_time": 338558.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a wire running down the middle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 338558.0,
      "end_time": 339998.0,
      "text": "and not only is it a wire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 339999.0,
      "end_time": 342359.0,
      "text": "if you take that piano circuit, you can thumbtack"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 342359.0,
      "end_time": 344298.0,
      "text": "into the middle of a pencil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 344298.0,
      "end_time": 347218.0,
      "text": "and you can lay out wire on the page, too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 347218.0,
      "end_time": 349639.0,
      "text": "and get electrical current to run through it."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 349639.0,
      "end_time": 351521.0,
      "text": "And so you can kind of hack a pencil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 351521.0,
      "end_time": 357420.0,
      "text": "just by thumbtacking into it with a little piano electrical circuit."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 357420.0,
      "end_time": 358982.0,
      "text": "And the electricity runs through your body too."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 358982.0,
      "end_time": 362328.0,
      "text": "And then you can take the little piano circuit off the pencil."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 362328.0,
      "end_time": 365782.0,
      "text": "You can make one of these brushes just on the fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 365782.0,
      "end_time": 367589.0,
      "text": "All you do is connect to the bristles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 367589.0,
      "end_time": 369581.0,
      "text": "and the bristles are wet, so they conduct,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 369581.0,
      "end_time": 372150.0,
      "text": "and the person&#39;s body conducts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 372150.0,
      "end_time": 374149.0,
      "text": "and leather is great to paint on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 374149.0,
      "end_time": 376854.0,
      "text": "and then you can start hooking to everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 376854.0,
      "end_time": 377849.0,
      "text": "even the kitchen sink."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 377849.0,
      "end_time": 379768.0,
      "text": "The metal in the sink is conductive."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 379768.0,
      "end_time": 383320.0,
      "text": "Flowing water acts like a theremin or a violin."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 383321.0,
      "end_time": 388303.0,
      "text": "(Musical notes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 388303.0,
      "end_time": 389557.0,
      "text": "And you can even hook to the trees."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 389557.0,
      "end_time": 392953.0,
      "text": "Anything in the world is either conductive or not conductive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 392953.0,
      "end_time": 394727.0,
      "text": "and you can use those together."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 394727.0,
      "end_time": 396183.0,
      "text": "So — (Laughter) —"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 396183.0,
      "end_time": 399337.0,
      "text": "I took this to those same teens, because those teens are"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 399338.0,
      "end_time": 401795.0,
      "text": "really awesome, and they&#39;ll try things that I won&#39;t try."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 401795.0,
      "end_time": 404778.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t even have access to a facial piercing if I wanted to."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 404778.0,
      "end_time": 408799.0,
      "text": "And this young woman, she made what she called a hula-looper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 408799.0,
      "end_time": 411212.0,
      "text": "and as the hula hoop traveled around her body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 411212.0,
      "end_time": 413983.0,
      "text": "she has a circuit taped to her shirt right there."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 413983.0,
      "end_time": 416240.0,
      "text": "You can see her pointing to it in the picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 416240.0,
      "end_time": 418440.0,
      "text": "And every time the hula hoop would smush against her body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 418440.0,
      "end_time": 420623.0,
      "text": "it would connect two little pieces of copper tape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 420623.0,
      "end_time": 422359.0,
      "text": "and it would make a sound, and the next sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 422359.0,
      "end_time": 424895.0,
      "text": "and it would loop the same sounds over and over again."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 424895.0,
      "end_time": 426823.0,
      "text": "I ran these workshops everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 426824.0,
      "end_time": 429834.0,
      "text": "In Taiwan, at an art museum, this 12-year-old girl"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 429834.0,
      "end_time": 433496.0,
      "text": "made a mushroom organ out of some mushrooms that were from Taiwan"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 433496.0,
      "end_time": 435280.0,
      "text": "and some electrical tape and hot glue."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 435280.0,
      "end_time": 437361.0,
      "text": "And professional designers were making artifacts"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 437361.0,
      "end_time": 439140.0,
      "text": "with this thing strapped onto it."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 439140.0,
      "end_time": 441354.0,
      "text": "And big companies like Intel"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 441354.0,
      "end_time": 445700.0,
      "text": "or smaller design firms like Ideo or startups like Bump,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 445700.0,
      "end_time": 446559.0,
      "text": "were inviting me to give workshops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 446559.0,
      "end_time": 448954.0,
      "text": "just to practice this idea of smashing electronics"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 448954.0,
      "end_time": 450786.0,
      "text": "and everyday objects together."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 450786.0,
      "end_time": 453447.0,
      "text": "And then we came up with this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 453447.0,
      "end_time": 455235.0,
      "text": "to not just use electronics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 455235.0,
      "end_time": 458207.0,
      "text": "but let&#39;s just smash computers with everyday objects"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 458207.0,
      "end_time": 460767.0,
      "text": "and see how that goes over."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 460767.0,
      "end_time": 464366.0,
      "text": "And so I just want to do a quick demo."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 464366.0,
      "end_time": 466991.0,
      "text": "So this is the MaKey MaKey circuit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 466991.0,
      "end_time": 469890.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m just going to set it up from the beginning in front of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 469890.0,
      "end_time": 473923.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ll just plug it in, and now it&#39;s on by USB."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 473923.0,
      "end_time": 476560.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll just hook up the forward arrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 476560.0,
      "end_time": 480100.0,
      "text": "You guys are facing that way, so I&#39;ll hook it to this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 480100.0,
      "end_time": 483647.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll just hook up a little ground wire to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 483647.0,
      "end_time": 486171.0,
      "text": "And now, if I touch this piece of pizza,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 486171.0,
      "end_time": 489235.0,
      "text": "the slides that I showed you before should go forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 489235.0,
      "end_time": 492667.0,
      "text": "And now if I hook up this wire just by connecting it"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 492667.0,
      "end_time": 495938.0,
      "text": "to the left arrow, I&#39;m kind of programming it by where I hook it up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 495939.0,
      "end_time": 498960.0,
      "text": "now I have a left arrow and a right arrow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 498960.0,
      "end_time": 501159.0,
      "text": "so I should be able to go forwards and backwards"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 501160.0,
      "end_time": 504264.0,
      "text": "and forwards and backwards. Awesome."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 504264.0,
      "end_time": 506808.0,
      "text": "And so we&#39;re like, \"We gotta put a video out about this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 506808.0,
      "end_time": 509376.0,
      "text": "Because no one really believed that this was important"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 509376.0,
      "end_time": 512355.0,
      "text": "or meaningful except me and, like, one other guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 512355.0,
      "end_time": 514390.0,
      "text": "So we made a video to prove that"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 514390.0,
      "end_time": 515579.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s lots of stuff you can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 515580.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517612.00000000006,
      "text": "You can kind of sketch with Play-Doh"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 517611.0,
      "end_time": 521545.0,
      "text": "and just Google for game controllers."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 521546.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524233.00000000006,
      "text": "Just ordinary Play-Doh, nothing special."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 524232.0,
      "end_time": 525934.0,
      "text": "And you can literally draw joysticks"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 525934.0,
      "end_time": 533570.0,
      "text": "and just find Pacman on your computer and then just hook it up. (Video game noises)"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 533570.0,
      "end_time": 536560.0,
      "text": "And you know the little plastic drawers you can get at Target?"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 536560.0,
      "end_time": 538767.0,
      "text": "Well, if you take those out, they hold water great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 538768.0,
      "end_time": 540904.0,
      "text": "but you can totally cut your toes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 540904.0,
      "end_time": 543592.0,
      "text": "so yeah, just be careful."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 543592.0,
      "end_time": 546464.0,
      "text": "You know the Happiness Project, where the experts"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 546464.0,
      "end_time": 549222.0,
      "text": "are setting up the piano stairs, and how cool that is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 549222.0,
      "end_time": 550432.0,
      "text": "Well, I think it&#39;s cool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 550432.0,
      "end_time": 552775.0,
      "text": "but we should be doing that stuff ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 552775.0,
      "end_time": 555858.0,
      "text": "It shouldn&#39;t be a set of experts engineering the way the world works."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 555858.0,
      "end_time": 557833.0,
      "text": "We should all be participating"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 557833.0,
      "end_time": 559752.0,
      "text": "in changing the way the world works together."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 559753.0,
      "end_time": 561940.0,
      "text": "Aluminum foil. Everybody has a cat."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 561940.0,
      "end_time": 565124.0,
      "text": "Get a bowl of water. This is just Photo Booth on your Mac OS."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 565124.0,
      "end_time": 567184.0,
      "text": "Hover the mouse over the \"take a photo\" button,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 567184.0,
      "end_time": 568759.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;ve got a little cat photo booth."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 568759.0,
      "end_time": 571448.0,
      "text": "And so we needed hundreds of people to buy this."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 571448.0,
      "end_time": 574536.0,
      "text": "If hundreds of people didn&#39;t buy this, we couldn&#39;t put it on the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 574536.0,
      "end_time": 577436.0,
      "text": "And so we put it up on Kickstarter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 577437.0,
      "end_time": 580432.0,
      "text": "and hundreds of people bought it in the first day."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 580432.0,
      "end_time": 581458.0,
      "text": "And then 30 days later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 581458.0,
      "end_time": 584725.0,
      "text": "11,000 people had backed the project."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 584725.0,
      "end_time": 586840.0,
      "text": "And then what the best part is, we started getting"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 586840.0,
      "end_time": 590912.0,
      "text": "a flood of videos in of people doing crazy things with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 590912.0,
      "end_time": 593574.0,
      "text": "So this is \"The Star-Spangled Banner\" by eating lunch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 593574.0,
      "end_time": 595647.0,
      "text": "including drinking Listerine."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 595648.0,
      "end_time": 597114.0,
      "text": "And we actually sent this guy materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 597114.0,
      "end_time": 598595.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re like, \"We&#39;re sponsoring you, man."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 598595.0,
      "end_time": 600705.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re, like, a pro maker.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 600705.0,
      "end_time": 604320.0,
      "text": "Okay, just wait for this one. This is good."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 604320.0,
      "end_time": 606139.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 606139.0,
      "end_time": 609624.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 609624.0,
      "end_time": 611501.0,
      "text": "And these guys at the exploratorium are"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 611501.0,
      "end_time": 614466.0,
      "text": "playing house plants as if they were drums."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 616723.0,
      "end_time": 620296.0,
      "text": "And dads and daughters are completing circuits in special ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 620297.0,
      "end_time": 622649.0,
      "text": "And then this brother -- look at this diagram."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 622649.0,
      "end_time": 623937.0,
      "text": "See where it says \"sister\"?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 623937.0,
      "end_time": 626393.0,
      "text": "I love when people put humans on the diagram."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 626393.0,
      "end_time": 628861.0,
      "text": "I always add humans to any technical --"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 628861.0,
      "end_time": 630992.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re drawing a technical diagram, put a human in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 630993.0,
      "end_time": 635463.0,
      "text": "And this kid is so sweet. He made this trampoline slideshow advancer for his sister"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 635463.0,
      "end_time": 637536.0,
      "text": "so that on her birthday, she could be the star of the show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 637536.0,
      "end_time": 640281.0,
      "text": "jumping on the trampoline to advance the slides."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 640281.0,
      "end_time": 643289.0,
      "text": "And this guy rounded up his dogs and he made a dog piano."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 646134.0,
      "end_time": 648579.0,
      "text": "And this is fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 648579.0,
      "end_time": 651465.0,
      "text": "and what could be more useful than feeling alive and fun?"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 651466.0,
      "end_time": 653986.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s also very serious because"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 653986.0,
      "end_time": 656154.0,
      "text": "all this accessibility stuff started coming up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 656154.0,
      "end_time": 659110.0,
      "text": "where people can&#39;t use computers, necessarily."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 659110.0,
      "end_time": 661802.0,
      "text": "Like this dad who wrote us, his son has cerebral palsy"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 661802.0,
      "end_time": 663674.0,
      "text": "and he can&#39;t use a normal keyboard."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 663674.0,
      "end_time": 667245.0,
      "text": "And so his dad couldn&#39;t necessarily afford"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 667245.0,
      "end_time": 669870.0,
      "text": "to buy all these custom controllers."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 669870.0,
      "end_time": 670713.0,
      "text": "And so, with the MaKey MaKey, he planned to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 670713.0,
      "end_time": 673607.0,
      "text": "these gloves to allow him to navigate the web."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 673607.0,
      "end_time": 675766.0,
      "text": "And a huge eruption of discussion"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 675767.0,
      "end_time": 678722.0,
      "text": "around accessibility came, and we&#39;re really excited about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 678722.0,
      "end_time": 680622.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t plan for that at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 680623.0,
      "end_time": 683431.0,
      "text": "And then all these professional musicians started using it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 683431.0,
      "end_time": 685559.0,
      "text": "like at Coachella, just this weekend"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 685559.0,
      "end_time": 688711.0,
      "text": "Jurassic 5 was using this onstage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 688711.0,
      "end_time": 692412.0,
      "text": "and this D.J. is just from Brooklyn, right around here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 692412.0,
      "end_time": 694423.0,
      "text": "and he put this up last month."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 694423.0,
      "end_time": 696527.0,
      "text": "And I love the carrot on the turntable."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 696527.0,
      "end_time": 703355.0,
      "text": "(Music: Massive Attack — \"Teardrop\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 703355.0,
      "end_time": 706101.0,
      "text": "Most people cannot play them that way. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 706101.0,
      "end_time": 707523.0,
      "text": "And when this started to get serious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 707523.0,
      "end_time": 710950.0,
      "text": "I thought, I&#39;d better put a really serious warning label on the box that this comes in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 710950.0,
      "end_time": 712652.0,
      "text": "because otherwise people are going to be getting this"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 712652.0,
      "end_time": 714891.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re going to be turning into agents of creative change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 714891.0,
      "end_time": 716183.0,
      "text": "and governments will be crumbling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 716183.0,
      "end_time": 718542.0,
      "text": "and I wouldn&#39;t have told people, so I thought I&#39;d better warn them."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 718542.0,
      "end_time": 720871.0,
      "text": "And I also put this little surprise. When you open the lid"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 720871.0,
      "end_time": 723731.0,
      "text": "of the box, it says, \"The world is a construction kit.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 723731.0,
      "end_time": 725578.0,
      "text": "And as you start to mess around this way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 725578.0,
      "end_time": 728677.0,
      "text": "I think that, in some small ways, you do start to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 728677.0,
      "end_time": 730729.0,
      "text": "the landscape of your everyday life"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 730729.0,
      "end_time": 733622.0,
      "text": "a little bit more like something you could express yourself with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 733622.0,
      "end_time": 735861.0,
      "text": "and a little bit more like you could participate"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 735861.0,
      "end_time": 738325.0,
      "text": "in designing the future of the way the world works."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 738325.0,
      "end_time": 742113.0,
      "text": "And so next time you&#39;re on an escalator"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 742113.0,
      "end_time": 743789.0,
      "text": "and you drop an M&M by accident,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 743789.0,
      "end_time": 746949.0,
      "text": "you know, maybe that&#39;s an M&M surfboard, not an escalator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 746949.0,
      "end_time": 748156.0,
      "text": "so don&#39;t pick it up right away."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 748156.0,
      "end_time": 750343.0,
      "text": "Maybe take some more stuff out of your pockets"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 750344.0,
      "end_time": 753653.0,
      "text": "and throw it down, and maybe some chapstick, whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 753653.0,
      "end_time": 758615.0,
      "text": "I used to want to design a utopian society"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 758615.0,
      "end_time": 760987.0,
      "text": "or a perfect world or something like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 760987.0,
      "end_time": 762440.0,
      "text": "But as I&#39;m kind of getting older"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 762441.0,
      "end_time": 764170.0,
      "text": "and kind of messing with all this stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 764170.0,
      "end_time": 766785.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m realizing that my idea of a perfect world"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 766785.0,
      "end_time": 768800.0,
      "text": "really can&#39;t be designed by one person"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 768801.0,
      "end_time": 770357.0,
      "text": "or even by a million experts."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 770357.0,
      "end_time": 773525.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really going to be seven billion pairs of hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 773525.0,
      "end_time": 775933.0,
      "text": "each following their own passions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 775933.0,
      "end_time": 778121.0,
      "text": "and each kind of like a mosaic coming up"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 778121.0,
      "end_time": 779622.0,
      "text": "and creating this world in their backyards"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 779622.0,
      "end_time": 781130.0,
      "text": "and in their kitchens."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 781130.0,
      "end_time": 783696.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the world I really want to live in."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 783696.0,
      "end_time": 785800.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 785800.0,
      "end_time": 790611.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}